data.description: 2/1 buy down is available on this home & it's eligible for USDA financing  Just outside the city limits west of Okmulgee sits an awesome 35-acre tract with 3 bedroom 2 bath ranch style home. Large covered deck for entertaining, 2-car garage, detached 1 car garage with 2 additional rooms attached that double as guest quarters / game room or office. Sellers believe Sq Ft Records don't reflect 2 additional spaces. HVAC new in 2022, Roof new in 2020. A big storm/root cellar, a shop with large loft area, and barn, and a pond. Large creek and small tributary meander through the property. Abuts a wildlife refuge with good hunting. 40 minutes to Tulsa Hills, 20 minutes to I-40, and 5 minutes to historic downtown Okmulgee. All this and country living under giant pine trees overlooking beautiful acreage with at least 50 mature pecan trees. Okmulgee Lake and Dripping Springs Lake are 10 minutes.
